        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Although my mind with Thine agrees:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "My being Thou dost own,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Some parts within would still not yield"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To say, “I’m Thine alone.”"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Remind me, Lord, of what love is,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "How faithfulness should be."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The universe to all declares"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thou lovest faithfully."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The heavens, spread from sky to sky,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Bespeak Thy boundless love;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Its vast dimensions, broad and high,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We’ll never fully prove."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "The vault of heav’n has billows soft;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "They tell Thy care for me;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Such gentle, kind and tender love"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Towards one so harsh towards Thee."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "5"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Surrounding range, majestic, sure,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy faithfulness displays."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Withstanding all, Thy love’s secure,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Immutable always."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "6"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For birds aloft and trees aground,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "What thorough care I see!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Thy loving care for me abounds"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "E’en more unceasingly."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "7"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Love vast, yet thorough; strong, yet sweet,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I praise with joyful tears;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I’ll love Thee, Lord, with all my heart"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Today and all my years."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "8"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Trustworthy, changeless, faithful, true—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I fain would learn from Thee,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "That with my heart, though weak, I too"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Can love Thee faithfully!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "9"
    }
  ],
